metadata.description: Each NFT (the MDAGREEN token) represents one kilo of açaí production. By purchasing the NFT, the buyer also has exclusive rights to remuneration from the sale of the açaí, which will be transferred from 3Agro. These rewards will be in the form of Moeda’s native token (MDA), which can be traded on crypto exchanges, used to purchase products and services, or to invest in Moeda’s wide array of socio-environmental projects supporting artisans, women-owned businesses, and more. Information available on https://3agro.com.br
